description:
Feng Shui World is the world’s leading magazine on feng shui, now brought to you on the iPad for an even more engaging media-rich experience. We bring you feature articles and commentary on lifestyle, property, fashion, home design and renovation, DIY feng shui, astrology, interviews with celebrities and other engaging personalities, and everything you need to know to improve your home, workplace & life to bring you an abundance of health, wealth and happiness.  

Helmed by the leading authority and internationally bestselling author on feng shui, Lillian Too, FSW for the iPad revolutionizes the practice of feng shui, making it easy-to-use and accessible to everyone. It is the most comprehensive and complete companion guide to feng shui and a great supplement to any books on the subject, allowing you to benefit from the dynamics of time dimension feng shui.  

Each issue includes 96 pages full of information accompanied by gorgeous photos, pictures and illustrations, allowing the reader to learn while at the same time be entertained. Purchase individual issues in your in-app Store and collect up your issues to build your library!

Auto Renewable Subscription Information 

Feng Shui World Magazine 1 year Subscription- £14.99 

Buy individual editions for £2.99

Payment will be charged to iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase

Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period

Account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period, and identify the cost of the renewal

Subscriptions may be managed by the user and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the user’s Account Settings after purchase

No cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during active subscription period
